  <section>
    <h2 id="methods">Core methods</h2>

    <div class="card-grid card-grid--2">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>ARAW (Assume Right / Assume Wrong)</h3>
        <p>Takes any claim and branches it: what follows if true? What follows if false? Then recurses &mdash; every conclusion becomes another claim to test. Results are stored in SQLite with leverage scores, crux detection, and domain classification.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>UAUA (Universalize &rarr; ARAW &rarr; Universalize &rarr; ARAW)</h3>
        <p>Four passes alternating between two operations:</p>
        <p><strong>Universalization</strong> asks "what is this an instance of?" and explores across the possibility space.</p>
        <p><strong>ARAW</strong> asks "is this true or false?" and tests claims through contradiction.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <pre><code>U1: Map the space &rarr; candidates
 &darr;
A1: Test candidates &rarr; validated/rejected
 &darr;
U2: Find edge cases of survivors &rarr; new candidates
 &darr;
A2: Final validation &rarr; what survived all rounds</code></pre>
  </section>

